### Variables
@host = http://localhost:3001
@basePath = /api/v1
# Reemplaza este token con uno real obtenido desde Cognito
@token = token_here

### ===========================================
### AUTHENTICATION ENDPOINTS (No requieren token)
### ===========================================

### Get Login URL
GET {{host}}{{basePath}}/auth/login
Accept: application/json

###

### Verify Token
POST {{host}}{{basePath}}/auth/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{token}}"
}

###

### Get Logout URL
GET {{host}}{{basePath}}/auth/logout
Accept: application/json

### ===========================================
### AUTHENTICATED ENDPOINTS (Requieren token)
### ===========================================

### Health Check (No requiere autenticaci√≥n)
GET {{host}}{{basePath}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Current User Info
GET {{host}}{{basePath}}/auth/me
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### COURSES
### ===========================================

### Get All Courses
GET {{host}}{{basePath}}/courses?lightDTO=true
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Course By ID
GET {{host}}{{basePath}}/courses/10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

